column5: A 5-year-old girl is playing in a river when she discovers then catches a large fish with her bare hands!!
I bet she won't top that PB in her life time! hahaha

That was originally on Americas Funniest Videos many years back.  The little girl in the video is a relation of an old friend.  That happened somewhere along the Indian river, or a small off chute of it.  Indian river leads into Rice lake.  The carp in the video was really out of it and was near death, hence the reason she was able to pick it up.  I think it won 2nd or 3rd place in the season finale of AFV - I think it was back in the mid '90's that happened.
Have you hugged your carp today?
